@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_vrduht(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.cos(0.06)
    v1 = v2
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.exp(wp.cos(v0 + 0.30)))
    v0 = (0.50 - wp.exp(tmp))
    v0 = (((v2 + 0.43 / tmp + 0.16) + wp.sin(tmp + 0.64)) * ((v2 + 0.16 * v2 + 0.28) - wp.abs(v0 + 0.79)))
    data[tid] = v0
